INTRODUCTION

Hoiana Resort & Golf offers a glamorous gathering place on the central Vietnam coast with various venue options for events and business meetings, as well as picturesque beachside settings for a wide range of wedding parties, events, and seminars. Our professional event planning and management team, along with our diverse culinary and customer service teams, ensure you will experience the utmost in luxury.

MICE Brochure
Request For Proposal

MEETING EVENT VENUES

BALLROOM

With its nine-meter high-ceilings, glittering mirrored walls and lustrous textured surfaces, the pillar-free Ballroom is a stately space worthy of lavish weddings, prestigious events and important conferences alike. With its moveable partition, the 515-square-meter ballroom can be divided into two spaces to cater to multi-purpose occasions.

Learn more

GREEN HOUSE

Located in the gardens, the Green House is a sparkling, sunlit, glass-walled venue equipped with a standalone pantry, flexible enough to host occasions ranging from memorable private dinners to convivial networking events and energizing breakout sessions.

Learn more

THE LAWN

Adjacent to the Ballroom, The Lawn provides ample space for scenic outdoor gatherings and is especially suitable for a picturesque wedding ceremony or cocktail reception amidst lush landscaping.

Learn more

THE LOFT

The Loft, our latest upscale meeting venue tailored to impress. Our guests can now experience the perfect blend of sophistication and serenity in the 240m2 contemporary indoor space, flooded with natural light through floor-to-ceiling glass doors. The 190m2 rooftop terrace features a stylish bar, verdant surroundings, and
panoramic ocean views with Cu Lao Cham Island on the horizon.

Learn more

THE SQUARE

The Square is a smaller, brighter venue connected to a terrace overlooking the lawn. The venue has an open kitchen that serves multiple functions. It can be used as a private preparation area for the bride and her entourage, or as a VIP lounge during corporate or social events.

Learn more

BEACH

Our beach wedding venue offers an idyllic coastal setting for your dream wedding. Nestled in our beachfront paradise, it showcases the natural elegance of Cham Island in the backdrop, with soft sands, breathtaking views, and a timeless atmosphere. This is the perfect location to exchange your vows against the
backdrop of endless horizons and a setting sun.

Learn more

BEACH LAWN

Provide the perfect backdrop for your dream wedding; our Beach Lawn features panoramic ocean views, lush greenery, and a serene atmosphere. This seaside haven offers a picturesque setting for your special day.

Learn more
